column5: Thanks for bringing them on board and also thanks to Ko-Man-Chi for the chance to be one of the Ontario anglers to prove thier baits.  You can click on Ko-Man-Chi in my sig. to see the awesome baits they have.Like TJ said,they are ground level,but there are alot of great products coming.   Thanks again Robert and TJ.  Now bring on the soft water.
Good stuff there Brian, I'm sure you'll do real well this year....soon you'll be giving seminars at the fishing shows  Maureen
Good Brian,thats wonderfull progress,I am sure you will help them well  marc
time for a complete boat and truck wrap
Misfish doing seminars? Who's gunna do the voice overs?  Way to go bud, they appear to have dynamite stuff.
LOL...  Thanks Misfish, many companiesa re seeing us as the place to get the word out quick!!
